            projects?</p>
        <br />
        <p><strong>Operations:</strong> The way the university operates is also extremely
            important to how
            it's survivability is affected. Is there any waste of energy? Is it clean and
            healthy to
            garantee the
            students safety? does it have proper insulation? etc.</p>
        <p>There are several operations that can be undertaken in order to promote/secure
